web pages:

    1. YSlow v2
        css:
            place the css styles at the top of the html document
            avoid certain css expressions
            minify the css files
        image:
            use desired image sizes instead of resizing within html using with and height attributes -> reduce the reponse size
            create sprites when possible -> reduce the number of images the browser required
        javascript:
            place javascript at the bottom of the html
            minify javascript
            make javascript external

        compress several files into single file


server optimization:
    1. YSlow v2
        whether the server utilize Gzip/bzip2 compression
        whether the DNS lookups are reduced
        whether the ETags are implemented